item.title: Say Cheese
item.description: ##23:57 Monday 05 January 2015 JST## I’ve solved up to level 24 on Say Cheese. My goal is to finish 25, so I’ll have done half of the levels before sending it to Fred. I can inconsistently do number 25 in eighteen moves, but they say it’s possible in sixteen moves. Hmm.
